 JavaScript Operators:

1) Arithmetic  Operators:
+ ,  -  ,   *  , 
Multiplication               -   *
Division                       -      /    (Q)
Modulus Operator        -     %   (R)
Exponential (raised to the power) -   **
++ , 
--     

   let a=10
        let b=5
           b++
           a--
           document.write(b ,"<br>")
           document.write(a ,"<br>")

        document.write(a%b ,"<br>") 
        //remainder part
        document.write(a/b ,"<br>") 
        //quotient
        document.write(a*b ,"<br>")
        document.write(a**b)
 
